languages.text: "Первый офицер Версериан, ни в коей мере — я привык не оставлять после себя следов. Но благодарю за ваше участие".
"Not at all, First Officer Werserian — I'm not in the habit of leaving a trail. But I thank you for your concern."

languages.text: 「とんでもない、ウェルセリアン副長殿…痕跡を残すような不手際はしない。だが、気遣いには感謝する」
languages.original_text: "Not at all, First Officer Werserian — I'm not in the habit of leaving a trail. But I thank you for your concern."

traits.locale_text: 「とんでもない、ウェルセリアン副長殿…痕跡を残すような不手際はしない。だが、気遣いには感謝する」

languages.text: “并非如此，韦尔森大副。我没有留下痕迹的习惯，但还是要感谢你的关心。”
languages.original_text: "Not at all, First Officer Werserian — I'm not in the habit of leaving a trail. But I thank you for your concern."

traits.locale_text: “并非如此，韦尔森大副。我没有留下痕迹的习惯，但还是要感谢你的关心。”

languages.text: «En absoluto, oficial primero Werserian. No tengo por costumbre dejar rastro, pero le agradezco su preocupación».
languages.original_text: "Not at all, First Officer Werserian — I'm not in the habit of leaving a trail. But I thank you for your concern."

traits.locale_text: «En absoluto, oficial primero Werserian. No tengo por costumbre dejar rastro, pero le agradezco su preocupación».

languages.text: « Absolument pas, second Werserian ; je n'ai pas pour habitude de laisser une piste derrière moi. Mais votre sollicitude me touche. »
languages.original_text: "Not at all, First Officer Werserian — I'm not in the habit of leaving a trail. But I thank you for your concern."

traits.locale_text: « Absolument pas, second Werserian ; je n'ai pas pour habitude de laisser une piste derrière moi. Mais votre sollicitude me touche. »

languages.text: "Mitnichten, Erster Offizier Werserian – ich habe nicht die Angewohnheit, Spuren zurückzulassen. Aber danke für Eure Besorgnis."
languages.original_text: "Not at all, First Officer Werserian — I'm not in the habit of leaving a trail. But I thank you for your concern."

traits.locale_text: "Mitnichten, Erster Offizier Werserian – ich habe nicht die Angewohnheit, Spuren zurückzulassen. Aber danke für Eure Besorgnis."

languages.text: "Hayır İkinci Kaptan Werserian. Ardımda iz bırakma alışkanlığım yoktur ama alakanız için teşekkür ederim."
languages.original_text: "Not at all, First Officer Werserian — I'm not in the habit of leaving a trail. But I thank you for your concern."

traits.locale_text: "Hayır İkinci Kaptan Werserian. Arkamda iz bırakma alışkanlığım yoktur. İlginiz için teşekkür ederim."
